prompt.title: Embedding for Embracing Simplicity in System Design
prompt.content: Simplicity also extends to the overall system design, encouraging the use of straightforward architectures and avoiding over-engineering. This approach helps in creating more robust and maintainable systems that can adapt to changing requirements over time.
